No. 11-5042. Michael J. Modena, Petitioner v. Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corporation, et al. 565 U.S. 934, 132 S. Ct. 381,

181 L. Ed. 2d 240,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6559. October 3, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
